summary: An adaptation of the Witch Elf Armour by Squizzo for UNPB-BBP with working weight slider. It requires Squizzo\'s original mod.
descriptionHtml:
An adaptation of the Witch Elf Armour by Squizzo for UNPB-BBP with working weight slider. It requires Squizzo\'s original mod.

This is my first modification. Any advice will be welcomed.

English is not my native language so sorry for my mistakes

Update 0.4: No pauldrons version added as an optional file
Update 0.5: No pauldrons this time, really

Required mods:
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/19319]Witch Elf Armour - UNP[/url]
The UNPB body replacer with BBP support: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37900/]UNPB REDUX PROJECT[/url] OR [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20227/]Troublemakers Clothing[/url]

Does not work without BBP.

Installation:
First install the required mods
Use NMM and overwrite when asked.
Manual installation: open archive, extract meshes folder into data folder and overwrite when asked.

Credits and thanks:
Squizzo for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/19319]Witch Elf Armour - UNP[/url]
calyps and xp32 and mrtroublemaker for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14899]UNP BLESSED BODY UNPB - With Optional BBP Breast Physics[/url]
dimon99 for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url]
author: belisariu
